Tokens

Class Resources

  • java.lang.Object
    • Tokens.Resources

  • public class Resources
extends java.lang.Object
    Object representation of resource costs, resources owned by players, and resources granted by structures or stages. The eight resource types are categorized by gold, raw materials and manufactured goods.
